<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Savoria Trading Co. | Premium Savoury Products</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;600;700;900&family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --blue: #1A4FBF;
    --blue-light: #2563EB;
    --blue-dark: #0F2D6B;
    --blue-pale: #EFF6FF;
    --blue-mid: #DBEAFE;
    --white: #FFFFFF;
    --off-white: #F8FAFF;
    --text-dark: #0F172A;
    --text-mid: #1E3A6E;
    --text-muted: #64748B;
    --border: rgba(26,79,191,0.15);
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    background: var(--white);
    color: var(--text-dark);
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* NAV */
  nav {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
    padding: 0 60px; height: 80px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.97);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(26,79,191,0.06);
    transition: box-shadow 0.3s;
  }
  .nav-logo {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--blue); letter-spacing: 2px; text-decoration: none;
  }
  .nav-logo span { color: var(--text-dark); }
  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 36px; list-style: none; }
  .nav-links a {
    color: var(--text-mid); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; transition: color 0.3s;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--blue); }
  .nav-cta { background: var(--blue); color: var(--white) !important; padding: 10px 22px; font-weight: 700 !important; }
  .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--blue-dark) !important; }

  /* HERO */
  #hero {
    min-height: 100vh; position: relative;
    display: flex; align-items: center;
    padding: 120px 60px 60px; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 65% 85% at 72% 50%, rgba(26,79,191,0.08) 0%, transparent 65%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 50% at 10% 85%, rgba(37,99,235,0.05) 0%, transparent 60%),
      linear-gradient(150deg, #FFFFFF 0%, #F0F6FF 100%);
  }
  .hero-grid-overlay {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(26,79,191,0.05) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(26,79,191,0.05) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 80px 80px;
  }
  .hero-shape {
    position: absolute; right: 5%; top: 12%; width: 460px; height: 460px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(26,79,191,0.09) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 2; max-width: 700px; }
  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(26,79,191,0.3); background: rgba(26,79,191,0.05);
    padding: 8px 18px; font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--blue); margin-bottom: 30px; animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease both;
  }
  .hero-badge::before { content: ''; width: 6px; height: 6px; background: var(--blue); border-radius: 50%; animation: pulse 2s infinite; }
  @keyframes pulse { 0%,100%{opacity:1;transform:scale(1)} 50%{opacity:0.5;transform:scale(1.3)} }
  .hero-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5.5rem);
    font-weight: 900; color: var(--text-dark); line-height: 1.05;
    margin-bottom: 24px; animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.2s ease both;
  }
  .hero-title .accent { color: var(--blue); display: block; }
  .hero-sub {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 520px; margin-bottom: 44px; animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.35s ease both;
  }
  .hero-btns { display: flex; gap: 18px; animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.5s ease both; }
  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--blue); color: var(--white); padding: 16px 36px;
    font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none; transition: background 0.3s;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--blue-dark); }
  .btn-secondary {
    border: 2px solid var(--blue); color: var(--blue); padding: 16px 36px;
    font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.3s;
  }
  .btn-secondary:hover { background: var(--blue); color: var(--white); }
  .hero-stats {
    position: absolute; right: 60px; bottom: 80px; display: flex; gap: 48px;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.6s ease both;
  }
  .stat-item { text-align: right; }
  .stat-num { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--blue); line-height: 1; }
  .stat-label { font-size: 0.6rem; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 4px; }
  .hero-line {
    position: absolute; right: 0; top: 0; bottom: 0; width: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, var(--blue), transparent); opacity: 0.2;
  }
  @keyframes fadeUp { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }

  /* SECTIONS */
  section { padding: 100px 60px; }
  .section-label {
    font-size: 0.62rem; letter-spacing: 4px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--blue);
    margin-bottom: 14px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px;
  }
  .section-label::before { content: ''; width: 30px; height: 2px; background: var(--blue); }
  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.2rem);
    font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-dark); line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .section-divider {
    width: 60px; height: 3px; border-radius: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--blue), var(--blue-light)); margin-bottom: 50px;
  }

  /* ABOUT */
  #about { background: var(--blue-pale); }
  .about-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 80px; align-items: center; }
  .about-image-block { position: relative; height: 520px; }
  .about-img-main {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue-mid), rgba(26,79,191,0.1));
    border: 1px solid rgba(26,79,191,0.2);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .about-img-main::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, transparent, transparent 20px, rgba(26,79,191,0.04) 20px, rgba(26,79,191,0.04) 21px);
  }
  .about-img-icon { font-size: 6rem; opacity: 0.2; }
  .about-badge-float {
    position: absolute; bottom: -20px; right: -20px;
    background: var(--blue); color: var(--white);
    padding: 24px 28px; text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(26,79,191,0.3);
  }
  .about-badge-float .num { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 2.4rem; font-weight: 900; line-height: 1; }
  .about-badge-float .txt { font-size: 0.6rem; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-top: 4px; }
  .about-text p { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.12rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.85; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .about-pillars { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; margin-top: 36px; }
  .pillar { border: 1px solid rgba(26,79,191,0.15); background: var(--white); padding: 20px; transition: all 0.3s; }
  .pillar:hover { border-color: var(--blue); box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(26,79,191,0.1); }
  .pillar-icon { font-size: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .pillar h4 { font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--blue); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .pillar p { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6; }

  /* TRADING */
  #trading { background: var(--white); }
  .trading-intro { max-width: 650px; margin-bottom: 64px; }
  .trading-intro p { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.8; }
  .trading-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 48px; }
  .trading-card {
    background: var(--off-white); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 40px 32px;
    border-top: 3px solid transparent; transition: all 0.3s;
  }
  .trading-card:hover { border-top-color: var(--blue); box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(26,79,191,0.1); transform: translateY(-4px); }
  .tc-num { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 900; color: rgba(26,79,191,0.08); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .tc-icon { font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .tc-title { font-size: 0.78rem; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--blue); margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .tc-desc { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; }
  .trading-process { background: var(--blue); padding: 48px; }
  .process-title { font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); margin-bottom: 36px; }
  .process-steps { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); position: relative; }
  .process-steps::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; top: 24px; left: 12%; right: 12%; height: 1px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); z-index: 0;
  }
  .process-step { text-align: center; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .step-dot {
    width: 48px; height: 48px; border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.5); border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto 16px;
    background: var(--blue); font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--white);
  }
  .step-name { font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); }

  /* PRODUCTS */
  #products { background: var(--blue-pale); }
  .products-tabs { display: flex; gap: 4px; margin-bottom: 48px; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--blue-mid); }
  .tab-btn {
    background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-muted);
    padding: 12px 24px; border-bottom: 2px solid transparent; margin-bottom: -2px; transition: all 0.3s;
  }
  .tab-btn.active { color: var(--blue); border-bottom-color: var(--blue); font-weight: 700; }
  .tab-btn:hover { color: var(--blue); }
  .products-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 24px; }
  .product-card { background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border); overflow: hidden; transition: all 0.3s; cursor: pointer; }
  .product-card:hover { border-color: var(--blue); transform: translateY(-6px); box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(26,79,191,0.15); }
  .product-img {
    height: 200px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue-mid), var(--blue-pale));
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 3.5rem; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .product-img::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: repeating-linear-gradient(-45deg, transparent, transparent 15px, rgba(26,79,191,0.04) 15px, rgba(26,79,191,0.04) 16px);
  }
  .product-tag { position: absolute; top: 14px; right: 14px; background: var(--blue); color: var(--white); font-size: 0.55rem; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 4px 10px; font-weight: 700; }
  .product-body { padding: 24px; }
  .product-name { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-dark); margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .product-desc { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .product-footer { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding-top: 16px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .product-origin { font-size: 0.62rem; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .product-link { font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--blue); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; }
  .product-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

  /* CLIENTELE */
  #clientele { background: var(--white); }
  .clients-intro { max-width: 600px; margin-bottom: 60px; }
  .clients-intro p { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.8; }
  .clients-logos { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 64px; }
  .client-logo {
    background: var(--off-white); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 36px 28px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; text-align: center; transition: all 0.3s;
  }
  .client-logo:hover { border-color: var(--blue); background: var(--blue-pale); box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(26,79,191,0.1); }
  .client-icon { font-size: 2rem; }
  .client-name { font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .testimonials { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 24px; }
  .testimonial { background: var(--blue-pale); padding: 40px; border-left: 4px solid var(--blue); position: relative; }
  .testimonial::before { content: '"'; font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 6rem; color: rgba(26,79,191,0.1); position: absolute; top: 10px; left: 24px; line-height: 1; }
  .testimonial p { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--text-mid); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 24px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .testimonial-author { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; }
  .author-avatar { width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 50%; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue-dark), var(--blue)); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1rem; color: var(--white); font-weight: 700; }
  .author-name { font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-dark); }
  .author-role { font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-muted); }

  /* CONTACT */
  #contact { background: var(--blue-pale); }
  .contact-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 80px; }
  .contact-info p { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 40px; }
  .contact-details { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; }
  .contact-item { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 16px; }
  .contact-icon { width: 40px; height: 40px; flex-shrink: 0; border: 1px solid rgba(26,79,191,0.25); background: var(--white); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1rem; }
  .contact-item-text h4 { font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--blue); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .contact-item-text p { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-mid); margin: 0; }
  .contact-form { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }
  .form-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; }
  .form-field { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
  .form-field label { font-size: 0.62rem; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--blue); font-weight: 600; }
  .form-field input, .form-field textarea, .form-field select { background: var(--white); border: 1px solid rgba(26,79,191,0.2); color: var(--text-dark); padding: 14px 16px; font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 0.85rem; outline: none; transition: border-color 0.3s; }
  .form-field input:focus, .form-field textarea:focus, .form-field select:focus { border-color: var(--blue); box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(26,79,191,0.08); }
  .form-field textarea { height: 120px; resize: vertical; }
  .form-submit { background: var(--blue); color: var(--white); border: none; padding: 16px 40px; font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; cursor: pointer; transition: background 0.3s; align-self: flex-start; }
  .form-submit:hover { background: var(--blue-dark); }

  /* FOOTER */
  footer { background: var(--blue-dark); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); padding: 60px; }
  .footer-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 48px; margin-bottom: 48px; }
  .footer-brand .nav-logo { display: block; margin-bottom: 16px; color: var(--white) !important; }
  .footer-brand .nav-logo span { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55) !important; }
  .footer-brand p { font-size: 0.82rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); line-height: 1.7; }
  .footer-col h4 { font-size: 0.62rem; letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .footer-col ul { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
  .footer-col ul a { font-size: 0.82rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.3s; }
  .footer-col ul a:hover { color: var(--white); }
  .footer-bottom { border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding-top: 28px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
  .footer-bottom p { font-size: 0.72rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35); }
  .footer-cert { display: flex; gap: 20px; }
  .cert-badge { font-size: 0.62rem; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); padding: 4px 10px; }

  /* REVEAL */
  .reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(40px); transition: all 0.7s ease; }
  .reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <a href="#" class="nav-logo">SAVORIA<span> TRADING CO.</span></a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#about">Company Profile</a></li>
    <li><a href="#trading">Trading Unit</a></li>
    <li><a href="#products">Products</a></li>
    <li><a href="#clientele">Clientele</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contact" class="nav-cta">Enquire Now</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<section id="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-grid-overlay"></div>
  <div class="hero-shape"></div>
  <div class="hero-line"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-badge">Established 2008 · Premium Trading</div>
    <h1 class="hero-title">The Art of<br><span class="accent">Savoury Excellence</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Sourcing, distributing and trading the world's finest savoury products — from artisan snacks to premium condiments — across global markets with uncompromising quality standards.</p>
    <div class="hero-btns">
      <a href="#products" class="btn-primary">Explore Products</a>
      <a href="#about" class="btn-secondary">Our Story</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-stats">
    <div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-num">250+</div><div class="stat-label">SKUs Traded</div></div>
    <div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-num">18</div><div class="stat-label">Countries</div></div>
    <div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-num">16yr</div><div class="stat-label">Industry Trust</div></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="about">
  <div class="about-grid">
    <div class="about-image-block reveal">
      <div class="about-img-main"><div class="about-img-icon">🫒</div></div>
      <div class="about-badge-float"><div class="num">A+</div><div class="txt">Quality Rated</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-text reveal">
      <div class="section-label">Company Profile</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Built on Integrity,<br>Driven by Flavour</h2>
      <div class="section-divider"></div>
      <p>Savoria Trading Co. is a leading specialist in the procurement, distribution, and wholesale trading of premium savoury food products. Founded in 2008, we have grown into a trusted partner for retailers, foodservice operators, and hospitality groups across Southern Africa and beyond.</p>
      <p>Our deep-rooted supplier relationships and rigorous quality assurance protocols ensure that every product we place carries our reputation — one built with care over sixteen years of dedicated industry service.</p>
      <div class="about-pillars">
        <div class="pillar"><div class="pillar-icon">🌍</div><h4>Global Sourcing</h4><p>Direct relationships with producers across 18 countries ensuring premium quality.</p></div>
        <div class="pillar"><div class="pillar-icon">🏆</div><h4>Quality Assured</h4><p>Every product undergoes strict QA checks before entering our supply chain.</p></div>
        <div class="pillar"><div class="pillar-icon">🤝</div><h4>Trusted Partners</h4><p>Long-term relationships with retailers, hotels, and food service chains.</p></div>
        <div class="pillar"><div class="pillar-icon">⚡</div><h4>Agile Logistics</h4><p>Flexible delivery solutions tailored to client volume and schedule requirements.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="trading">
  <div class="trading-intro reveal">
    <div class="section-label">Trading Unit</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">How We Trade</h2>
    <div class="section-divider"></div>
    <p>Our dedicated trading unit operates as a full-spectrum procurement and distribution engine. From identifying emerging product categories to negotiating favourable terms and executing last-mile delivery, we handle the complete value chain so our clients don't have to.</p>
